title: Tim Barry from Avail
itunes:title: Tim Barry from Avail
description:
Tim Barry. Avail. I am so stoked to type these words to you as I had a lengthy conversation with the vocalist of Avail, Tim Barry. This band is truly special and we discuss all things Avail, reunions, instinct and living frugally. He's such a gem of a human I can't wait for you to dive in and listen.
